Class AbstractStockHolder

java.lang.Object
net.okocraft.box.api.model.stock.AbstractStockHolder
All Implemented Interfaces:
StockHolder
@Deprecated(since="5.5.0", forRemoval=true) @ScheduledForRemoval(inVersion="6.0.0") public abstract class AbstractStockHolder extends Object implements StockHolder
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
This class will be removed in Box 6.0.0
An abstract implementation of StockHolder.

The UserStockHolder returned by StockManager.loadUserStock(BoxUser) or BoxPlayer.getUserStockHolder() extends this abstract class.
